title: Elders of Brood's Last Raid.avi
description:
Elders of Brood, a WoW guild that has been active for almost 2.5 years has ended it&#039;s raiding days. To "celebrate" this event we did one final raid in the same place it all began: Molten Core.

I would like to thank all people who made this possible, especially "Wildfire" the heart and soul of the guild.


Again, i uploaded this torrent mainly for the people in the guild, but if you&#039;re interested please feel free to download it.
